OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some mist
OL,6,Fand fog. But cloud will lift quickly,
OL,7,Fleaving a fine and dry day for all
OL,8,Fwith lengthy sunshine. This can turn
OL,9,Fhazy in the east, but feeling warm
OL,10,Fthroughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA very clear night to come
OL,13,Fwith calm winds expected. Mist and fog
OL,14,Fpatches forming in the east with
OL,15,Ftemperatures falling close to
OL,16,Ffreezing, forming a grass from in
OL,17,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
